snippet.title: The Tarnishing of Juxtia - Wishlist Now on Steam
snippet.description:
The Tarnishing of Juxtia is glad to announce it will be coming to Steam on PC! Thank you everyone for all of your support! Add to your Wishlist now and follow us on Steam for future updates.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1428710/The_Tarnishing_of_Juxtia/
